      "name": "NOMADS",
      "description": "A cybercrime group of at least 4 members (Chernuha, Forust/MrForust, Hudan, Xdfnx) operating the MefStealer information stealer. Likely based in Slovakia based on residential IP evidence. Members have backgrounds in CTF competitions, web pentesting, and system administration.",
